sg.edu.nus.cs2020

Class LeafNode<KType>

  • java.lang.Object
    • sg.edu.nus.cs2020.TreeNode<KType>
      • sg.edu.nus.cs2020.LeafNode<KType>
  • Type Parameters:
    KType - the type of leaf value

    public class LeafNode<KType>
extends TreeNode<KType>
    This is a node class that is designed specifically to be a leaf of the tree. It cannot have any children and it is used to hold the object name. It has one additional field m_object that stores the object.
